    PQuery, PQueryHeader

    public class GenericTracedPQuery
extends GenericReferencedPQuery
    This PQuery class defines an extended query for the given referenced query with the additional trace object. 
    pattern baseQuery<referenced><traced>(<base parameters>, <referenced parameters>, <trace>)
    Required to select matches based on the notification of the Trace object.
    Author:
    Csaba Debreceni
